item.title: 040 - Moving on From California
item.description: Today is my last day in California. I’m sitting in the SFO airport waiting for my flight back east to board. Figured it was a good time to write a word vomit. Maybe process some stuff that I’m feeling. The thing is I’m not feeling anything significant. I’m excited to go back east, back home, is really how I think about it. I never got to feel like Cali was home.
